\c 33
\s Ukubuyisana kukaJakobe loEsawu
\p
\v 1 UJakobe wasephakamisa amehlo akhe, wabona, khangela-ke, uEsawu esiza lamadoda angamakhulu amane kanye laye\x + 32.6.\x*. Wasesehlukanisa abantwana phakathi kukaLeya loRasheli lencekukazi zombili.
\v 2 Wasebeka izincekukazi labantwana bazo ngaphambili, loLeya labantwana bakhe ngemuva, loRasheli loJosefa ekucineni.
\v 3 Yena uqobo wasesedlula phambi kwabo, wakhothamela emhlabathini\x + 18.2; 42.6; 43.26.\x* kasikhombisa waze wafika eduze lomnewabo.
\v 4 UEsawu wasegijima ukumhlangabeza, wamgona\x + 32.28.\x*, wawela entanyeni yakhe, wamanga\x + 45.14.\x*; basebekhala inyembezi.
\v 5 Wasephakamisa amehlo akhe wabona abesifazana labantwana, wathi: Ngobani laba olabo? Wasesithi: Abantwana uNkulunkulu ngomusa ayinike bona inceku yakho\x + 48.9. Hlab. 127.3. Isa. 8.18.\x*.
\v 6 Zasezisondela incekukazi, zona labantwana bazo, bakhothama.
\v 7 Laye uLeya wasesondela labantwana bakhe, bakhothama; emva kwalokho uJosefa wasondela loRasheli, bakhothama.
\v 8 Wasesithi: Uqondeni\f + \fk uqondeni: \fl Heb. \fq liyini leliqembu kuwe.\f* \add ngaleli\add* iqembu lonke\x + 32.16.\x* engihlangene lalo? Wasesithi: Ukuthola umusa emehlweni enkosi yami\x + 32.5; 33.15.\x*.
\v 9 UEsawu wasesithi: Ngilokunengi, mfowethu; okwakho kakube ngokwakho.
\v 10 UJakobe wasesithi: Hayi bo! Uba khathesi ngithole umusa emehlweni akho, yemukela isipho sami esivela esandleni sami; ngoba yikho\x + 18.5; 19.8.\x* ngibone ubuso bakho \add ku\add*njengokuthi ngibone ubuso bukaNkulunkulu\x + 2 Sam. 14.32. Mat. 18.10.\x*, njalo wathokoza ngami.
\v 11 Ake wemukele isipho\f + \fk isipho: \fl Heb. \fq isibusiso.\f* sami esilethwa kuwe\x + Hlu. 1.15. 1 Sam. 25.27; 30.26. 2 Kho. 5.15.\x*; ngoba uNkulunkulu ungiphile ngomusa, njalo ngoba ngilakho konke. Wasemncenga, waze wa\add s\add*emukela\x + 19.3. 2 Sam. 13.25,27. 2 Kho. 5.23.\x*.
\v 12 Wasesithi: Asisuke sihambe, njalo ngizahamba phambi kwakho.
\v 13 Kodwa wathi kuye: Inkosi yami iyazi ukuthi abantwana babuthakathaka, lokuthi izimvu lezinkomo engilazo ziyenyisa; uba-ke beziqhuba ngamandla usuku olulodwa, umhlambi wonke uzakufa.
\v 14 Inkosi yami ake yedlule phambi kwenceku yayo; mina-ke ngizaqhubeka kuhle kuhle\x + 2 Sam. 18.5. Isa. 8.6.\x*, ngokuhamba\f + \fk ngokuhamba: \fl Heb. \fq ngonyawo.\f* komsebenzi ophambi kwami, langokuhamba kwabantwana, ngize ngifike enkosini yami eSeyiri\x + 33.16; 32.3.\x*.
\v 15 UEsawu wasesithi: Ake ngibeke kuwe okwabantu abalami. Wasesithi: Kungani lokhu? Kangithole umusa emehlweni enkosi yami\x + 33.8; 34.11; 47.25. Ruthe 2.13.\x*.
\p
\v 16 UEsawu wasebuyela ngendlela yakhe ngalolosuku, waya eSeyiri.
\v 17 Njalo uJakobe waqhubeka waya eSukothi\x + Josh. 13.27. Hlu. 8.5. Hlab. 60.6.\x*\f + \fk iSukothi: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq amadumba.\f*, wazakhela indlu, wenzela izifuyo zakhe izibaya ezilophahla; ngakho wayitha ibizo lendawo iSukothi.
\p
\v 18 UJakobe wasefika evikelekile emzini weShekema\x + Josh. 24.1. Hlu. 9.1 Hlab. 60.6.\x*, oselizweni leKhanani, ekuveleni kwakhe ePadani-Arama; wamisa inkamba phambi komuzi.
\v 19 Njalo ingxenye yesiqinti amisela kuyo amathente akhe wayithenga esandleni samadodana kaHamori uyise kaShekema\x + Josh. 24.32. Joha. 4.5.\x*, ngezinhlamvu zemali ezilikhulu.
\v 20 Wasemisa khona ilathi, walibiza ngokuthi yiEli-Elohe-Israyeli\x + 35.7.\x*\f + \fk iEli-Elohe-Israyeli: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq uNkulunkulu uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli.\f*.
